<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">At Teamwork Commerce, we partner with industry leaders to bring cutting-edge solutions to our clients. Our collaboration with Bluebird introduces the RFR 901 Handheld UHF RFID Reader, paired with iPhone capabilities, to streamline inventory management and boost operational efficiency. Here's how this partnership helps retailers stay ahead.</p>

<h2>Real-time stock accuracy with exceptional RFID performance</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Together, Teamwork Commerce and Bluebird bring unmatched precision to inventory tracking. The RFR 901, equipped with advanced UHF RFID technology, can detect tags from up to 10 meters away and process up to 1,300 tags per second for fast, accurate stock counts. That combination helps retailers maintain real-time stock accuracy, improving operational efficiency and minimizing discrepancies.</p>

<h2>Seamless integration with Teamwork POS</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Inventory data captured by the RFR 901 syncs instantly with the Teamwork Commerce POS system, keeping stock records accurate and current. Using iPhone and iPad together, staff can capture, review, and finalize count memos, streamlining the entire stock count process into one connected workflow rather than a separate, disconnected step.</p>

<h2>Ergonomic design for all-day productivity</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Long shifts demand tools that are functional and comfortable. At just 353 grams with an ergonomic pistol grip, the RFR 901 is designed to reduce strain during extended use. Paired with Teamwork Commerce's software on iPhone and iPad, it's built to support productivity without adding to employee fatigue.</p>

<h2>Boost productivity with programmable versatility</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Retail environments are dynamic, and the RFR 901 adapts to match. Its programmable trigger lets staff toggle between RFID scanning, 1D/2D barcode scanning, and combination scanning — handling any inventory task with a single device.</p>

<h2>Tailored inventory management for retailers</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">The solution also offers customizable inventory zones, letting retailers define stock tracking by store layout or region. That means faster, more accurate counts and precision across multi-store operations, ensuring every item is accounted for no matter how many locations a retailer runs.</p>

<h2>Bluebird at GITEX Global 2025</h2>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Teamwork Commerce is proud to celebrate our partner Bluebird at GITEX Global 2025, where Bluebird will showcase its retail technology at one of the world's largest tech events in Dubai. It's a strong opportunity to see how these solutions are shaping the future of retail on a global stage.</p>
